
  Doublade    Steel Type Pokémon

  When Honedge evolves, it divides 
  into two swords, which cooperate 
  via telepathy to coordinate attacks 
  and slash their enemies to ribbons. 
  
	   Evolution Chain
  Honedge ► Doublade ► Aegislash

